name: KaelvinSmix+
description:
this was supposed to be my patreon model, but after thinking about my ideals of a free AI for all, I decided to post it here for everyone to use.

So please, Enjoy and post all your results here, or at my social media!

My custom model! Still using KaelvinSmix with base to train, thanks for the create of the greats model that are use as base for this one.

You can found more images at the model's discord.

You can follow my on instagram

Below a hello for portuguese/brazilian folks out there:

Olá meus caros amigos brasileiros e portugueses, tudo bem?

Se você quiser uma comunidade para conversar sobre/divulgar suas artes e ideias sobre IA, considere a entrar no discord. Vamos nos unir =D.

P.s (that include NSFW images, so use with caution).

If you are looking for something more explicit, try kaelvinSmixHC

I don't own any model used in this merged, so:

All rights goes to them.

I just upload it here, for those who like to test it.
